org.eclipse.emf.compare.util
Class EFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.eclipse.emf.compare.util.EFactory

public class EFactory
extends java.lang.Object

This is a factory for an ecore metamodel. There is a factory by package. Each factory is used to create instances of classifiers.

eInstanceOf

public static boolean eInstanceOf(EObject object,
                                  java.lang.String name)
Indicates if the object is instance of the class whose name is given.

Samples :

An instance of java.resources.Folder return true if name equals "Folder" or "resources.Folder".

An instance of java.resources.Folder return true if name equals "File" and Folder inherits File.

Parameters:
object - is the object
name - is the class name
Returns:
true if the object is instance of the class whose name is given
